msgctxt "body.0255c58d-adde-44ee-aa6f-5c1bc2736f25"
msgid "Travel Support"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.0255c58d-adde-44ee-aa6f-5c1bc2736f25"
msgid ""
"A limited travel fund is available for session hosts whose session proposals are accepted through our Call for Proposals. <b>We are unable to offer travel support for general participants or "
"volunteers.</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.0255c58d-adde-44ee-aa6f-5c1bc2736f25"
msgid ""
"If you have an idea for a session, we encourage you to submit a proposal even if you don't currently have travel funding lined up. Travel support is reviewed as part of the selection process and "
"session hosts who need support can request it then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.0255c58d-adde-44ee-aa6f-5c1bc2736f25"
msgid "Please note that funds are limited and support is not guaranteed for every accepted facilitator."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "Welcome to Fabra i Coats"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "Mozilla Festival 2026 is happening in Barcelona, Spain, from October 28-30 at Recinte Fabra i Coats."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid ""
"Originally built in the nineteenth century as a textile factory, the space today is an institution dedicated to the research, production, exhibition and dissemination of contemporary artistic "
"practices."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid ""
"Located in the Sant Andreu, a formerly independent village in the norther part of Barcelona, it’s easy to reach by metro, bus, or taxi. It retains it's industrial vibe with a mix of historic, narrow"
" and winding streets filled with independent and boutique stores as well as attractions including the Church of Sant Andreu de Palomar and the Antoni Gaudí designed mosaic floor at Sant Pacià "
"Church."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "<b>Address:<br/></b><i>Carrer de Sant Adrià,<br/>Sant Andreu, 08030<br/>Barcelona, Spain</i>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.right_column.08a8a99a-5861-417e-90fb-1b61c0a816c9.image.alt_text"
msgid "Fabra i Coats: brick industrial buildings with a tall chimney and graffiti, under a blue sky."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid "Accessibility, Inclusion &amp; Wellbeing"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid ""
"MozFest is meant to be for everyone. We want it to be welcoming, navigable, and as safe as possible for all — across all genders, sexualities, faiths, abilities, and backgrounds. We have been "
"working closely with the venue and our production team to plan for the following:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid ""
"A <b>marked accessible route</b> runs through the campus, avoiding cobblestoned areas. The full route map will be published ahead of the festival. By mobility scooter, the longest journey across the"
" venue takes about 4 minutes, and the nearest metro station is about 3 minutes away"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid "<b>Elevators are available in all main festival buildings</b> and have been tested for mobility device user access and control"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid ""
"Most <b>restrooms at the venue are gender neutral</b>. Accessible restrooms are also available and will be marked on the venue map In planning are the following designated spaces for specific "
"participant wellbeing needs:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid "A <b>quiet space away from high traffic areas</b> with comfortable seating and designated as fragrance-free"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid "A <b>multi-faith space</b> for anyone who wishes to observe faith-based customs during the festival"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid "A <b>first aid station</b> staffed by trained medical professionals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid "If you have access needs we should know about or questions you'd like to talk through, please email <a id=\"a1\">festival@mozillafoundation.org</a> in advance so we can plan with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.e0b2ee9d-76c4-47e5-bc8b-e8425eb29a51"
msgid ""
"Our Safety Team will be on hand throughout the venue to handle any reports of Community Participation Guidelines violations. You can contact them confidentially at any information point, or by "
"calling a dedicated reporting number that will be shared closer to the event."
msgstr ""
